org.apache.ctakes.ytex.kernel.evaluator

Class SemanticTypeKernel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.ytex.kernel.evaluator.CacheKernel
      • org.apache.ctakes.ytex.kernel.evaluator.SemanticTypeKernel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Kernel

    public class SemanticTypeKernel
extends CacheKernel
    Before comparing semantic distance, use this kernel to filter by semantic type.

    Modes:

  • MAINSUI (default): concept's main semantic types must overlap
  • TUI: concept's TUIs must overlap.

    The MAINSUI mode is taken from Sujeevan Aseervatham's semantic kernel. It maps all semantic types to a handful of semantic types.

    The corpusName parameter specifies the concepts for which cuis' semantic types will be loaded
